					</p>
		<div class="comment-content">
			<p>Hi Yeom,</p>
<p>To adjust the line width, use the <a href="https://ctan.org/pkg/geometry?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">geometry package</a>. See <a href="https://texblog.org/2012/03/01/latex-page-line-and-font-settings/">this post</a> for a short introduction.</p>
<p>I hope this answers your question.</p>
<p>Best,<br />
Tom</p>
